== Umuhanda mushyashya wa Ngoma-bugesera-Nyanza ==
Reta y'  [[Rwanda|Urwanda]]<ref>[[Rwanda]]</ref> yatangije umushinga wo kubaka umuhanda muremure uva [[Kigali]]  werekeza Mukarere ka ngoma<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/Umuhanda-wa-kaburimbo-Ngoma-Bugesera-Nyanza-uzoroshya-ubuhahirane</ref> ndetse na bugesera kandi ugahura n'Akarere ka Nyanza  , ukazafasha  bikomenye abaturage bo mu karere ka Nyanza<ref>[[Akarere ka Nyanza]]</ref> muntara y' amajyepfo<ref>[[Intara y'amajyepfo]]</ref> uyu muhanda werekeza Nyanza  urimo gusozwa Abanyarwanda bavugako uyumuhanda uzabafasha byinshi mubijyanye niterambere ryuturere twombi ndetse nigihugu muri Rusange.

== Umushinga w'ubwubatsi ==
[[Dosiye:A_road_down_and_up.jpg|thumb|Ubwiza butatse imihanda yo mu Rwanda cyane irimo kubakwa ]]
Uyu muhanda werekeza nyanza watewe inkunga ikomeye na leta y' Urwanda<ref>government of Rwanda [https://www.gov.rw/]</ref> kubufaranye na Minisiteri y ibikorwa remezo<ref>https://www.rba.co.rw/post/MININFRA-yasinze-imihigo-yo-kwagura-no-kubungabunga-ibikorwa-remezo</ref> kunkunga ya leta y ubushinwa .

== Amateka ==
Mbere y' umwaka wa 2020 ntamuha uhuza akarere ka Nyanza na Bugesera war'  uhari ubundi ubajya Mumajyepfo ahoa bakunze kwita Kumayaga bakoresga umuhanda wa Kigali Nyabugogo-Muhanga yahoze ari '''Gitarama'''<ref>https://www.muhanga.gov.rw/</ref> , gusa iyo nzira yari Ndende.

